yarn init -y
yarn add -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite
npx tailwindcss init -p
create a folder called css and add a file called tailwind.css inside then paste the code below inside it.

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

add the following line to package.json 

"scripts": {
    "dev": "vite"
  },


finally run the command npm run dev in your terminal.

